  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p701396/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201402/38151e1ad7ac4ca1945ce4ccf2dfa6f1.jpg\" style=\"width: 460px; height: 282px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英乐天天唱》是一档模仿唱歌类节目，目的在于提升大家的英语口语能力。主持人会在每期节目中选取好听的歌曲片段，并给出发音提示和模仿示例。喜欢听音乐的童鞋可要积极参与哦</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>歌曲简介：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t熟悉电影&lt;诺丁山&gt;的同学一定对电影中那首插曲she不陌生了,这是这首歌曲成就了&lt;诺&gt;的经典,成为其不可分割的一部分,这首歌也Elvis Costello为全球影迷所熟知,推动他演艺生涯又一个春天的到来。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>全曲欣赏：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p701396\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">模唱歌词：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tshe may be the face I can't forget<br />\n\ta trace of pleasure I regret<br />\n\tmay be my <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/treasure\" target=\"_blank\">treasure</a> or the price I have to pay<br />\n\tshe may be the song that Summer sings<br />\n\tmay be the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/chill\" target=\"_blank\">chill</a> that autumn brings<br />\n\tmy be a hundred different things<br />\n\twithin the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/measure\" target=\"_blank\">measure</a> of the day.<br />\n\tshe may be the beauty or the beast<br />\n\tmay be the famine or the feast<br />\n\tmay turn each day into heaven or a hell<br />\n\tshe may be the mirror of my dream<br />\n\ta smile reflected in a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stream\" target=\"_blank\">stream</a><br />\n\tshe may not be what she may seem<br />\n\tinside her shell&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>音频讲解：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p701396\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_v