  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.fpwap.com/UploadFiles/sjrj/2012/9/201296114519.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 196px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p700419\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tIndia's launching a new Super League Football <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Championship\" target=\"_blank\">Championship</a>. Some of the country's most famous personalities like former <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cricketer\" target=\"_blank\">cricketers</a> Sachin Tendulkar and Sourav Ganguly have bought teams along with a number of Bollywood stars. The All India Football Federation says eight teams will compete in the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/league\" target=\"_blank\">league</a> which is due to kick off in September. It's open to raise a profile of football in India where cricket is hugely popular. Spanish football club Atl&eacute;tico Madrid will be part of the Kolkata team. Rahul Tandon reports from Kolkata.</p>\n<p>\n\tHere in India, it's all about football now, not cricket. The players who's coming in, Henry looks like he could be part of the league. Dwight Yorke's coming in, Hern&aacute;n Crespo as well, the great Argentinian <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/striker\" target=\"_blank\">striker</a>. I think we're gonna see more and more names added over the next week or so, particularly of these big owners who will come in. I've been speaking to one of them Sourav Ganguly and asking him how big could this league be?</p>\n<p>\n\tIndia's a global player in <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cricket\" target=\"_blank\">cricket</a>. They are not a global player in football. But I think this is a step forward. This is gonna take time, but I think someday this will also be very popular.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Verdana, Arial; line-height: 1.8em;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江英语&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p700419/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p700419\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p701686/\">那些离死神越来越近的坏习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p700810/\">测试：你属于男性大脑还是女性大脑</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p488758/\">强化直达：两个月突破四六级新题型！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p516284/\">英音控必看：十大经典迷你剧推荐</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p701381/\">老奶奶114岁，Facebook说没准备好</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p701644/\">闻香识人心 出轨者最常用10款香水</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p701220/\">食堂太难吃 校长请来米其林大厨</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p594918/\">99%的人连Where are you from都不会回答！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p701682/\">数学证明热气球吓跑猪 英农民获赔4万英镑</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/